查看操作系统版本
lsb_release -a 

aliyun的ecs，增加数据盘后，将磁盘挂载到系统
mkdir /mnt/dat/
mount /dev/xvdb /mnt/dat/

设置为开机自动挂载
vi /etc/fstab
增加如下行
/dev/xvdb	/mnt/dat/	ext3	dos 	0	0

yum install git

yum install gcc-c++

yum install openssl openssl-devel 

CentOS下安装man手册
yum install -y man man-pages

安装图片验证码的支持库
yum install gd gd-devel

安装正则表达式的支持库
yum install boost boost-devel

 yum install log4cxx-devel log4cxx
 
 yum install fcgi fcgi-devel
 
 yum install apr apr-devel
 
 yum install mysql++-devel mysql++
 
 安装cgicc的支持
  wget http://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/cgicc/cgicc-3.2.10.tar.gz
  
  tar zxvf cgicc-3.2.10.tar.gz
  cd cgicc-3.2.10
  ./configure --prefix=$HOME/workspace/SOFT/cgicc-3.2.10
  make;make install
  
  
  ln -s  /home/release/workspace/SETUP/lab_of_2012/SOFT/CGICC/build/ ./SOFT/cgicc 

yum install docker

